="19.274">one</span> <span begin="19.274" end="20.329">else</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我与他人共度的时光 都是徒然浪费</span></p><p begin="21.803" end="24.439" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="21.803" end="22.203">She</span> <span begin="22.203" end="22.421">was</span><span begin="22.421" end="22.586">n&apos;t</span> <span begin="22.642" end="22.942">e</span><span begin="22.942" end="23.066">ven</span> <span begin="23.193" end="23.614">half</span> <span begin="23.614" end="24.115">of</span> <span begin="24.115" end="24.439">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">她甚至不及你半分</span></p><p begin="25.628" end="29.762" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="25.628" end="25.871">Rem</span><span begin="25.871" end="26.111">i</span><span begin="26.111" end="26.638">niscin&apos;</span> <span begin="26.638" end="26.833">how</span> <span begin="26.833" end="27.075">you</span> <span begin="27.075" end="27.938">felt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">回想着你当初的感觉</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="28.042" end="29.762"><span begin="28.042" end="28.559">(-niscin&apos;</span> <span begin="28.559" end="28.776">how</span> <span begin="28.776" end="28.972">you</span> <span begin="28.972" end="29.762">felt)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">想着你当初的感觉</span></span></p><p begin="30.671" end="35.751" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="30.671" end="30.939">And</span> <span begin="30.939" end="31.470">e</span><span begin="31.470" end="31.918">ven</span> <span begin="31.918" end="32.261">though</span> <span begin="33.651" end="33.891">you</span> <span begin="33.891" end="34.141">put</span> <span begin="34.141" end="34.410">my</span> <span begin="34.410" end="34.631">life</span> <span begin="34.631" end="34.936">through</span> <span begin="34.936" end="35.751">hell</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">尽管你让我的人生坠入地狱</span></p><p begin="37.547" end="40.877" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="37.547" end="37.802">I</span> <span begin="37.802" end="38.002">can&apos;t</span> <span begin="38.002" end="38.212">seem</span> <span begin="38.271" end="38.394">to</span> <span begin="38.515" end="38.732">for</span><span begin="38.781" end="39.151">get</span> <span begin="39.301" end="39.743">&apos;bout</span> <span begin="39.743" end="40.042">you,</span> <span begin="40.254" end="40.706">&apos;bout</span> <span begin="40.706" end="40.877">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我依然对你念念不忘</span></p><p begin="41.479" end="43.631" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="41.479" end="41.729">I</span> <span begin="41.729" end="41.931">want</span> <span begin="41.931" end="42.135">you</span> <span begin="42.135" end="42.323">to</span> <span begin="42.421" end="42.639">my</span><span begin="42.639" end="43.631">self</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">全身心地渴望着你</span></p><p begin="45.353" end="49.709" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="45.353" end="45.610">And</span> <span begin="45.610" end="45.835">now</span> <span begin="45.835" end="46.081">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="46.081" end="46.361">ask</span><span begin="46.361" end="46.559">in&apos;,</span> <span begin="46.559" end="46.690">who</span> <span begin="46.690" end="46.956">do</span> <span begin="46.956" end="47.277">you</span> <span begin="47.306" end="47.552">be</span><span begin="47.552" end="47.901">long</span> <span begin="48.009" end="48.462">to</span> <span begin="48.531" end="49.709">now?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我心中疑问 此刻谁拥有着你？</span></p><p begin="50.470" end="53.621" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="50.470" end="50.704">Who</span> <span begin="50.704" end="50.896">you</span> <span begin="50.945" end="51.149">give</span> <span begin="51.198" end="51.409">that</span> <span begin="51.448" end="51.850">love</span> <span begin="51.886" end="52.417">to</span> <span begin="52.417" end="53.621">now?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你的爱给了谁？</span></p><p begin="54.378" end="57.738" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="54.378" end="54.572">Who</span> <span begin="54.572" end="54.827">you</span> <span begin="54.903" end="55.299">pullin&apos;</span> <span begin="55.341" end="56.317">u</span><span begin="56.317" end="57.738">p on?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你会去谁那里拜访？</span></p><p begin="58.282" end="1:01.304" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="58.282" end="58.536">Who</span> <span begin="58.536" end="58.719">you</span> <span begin="58.771" end="59.002">get</span><span begin="59.002" end="59.175">tin&apos;</span> <span begin="59.175" end="59.679">sprung</span> <span begin="59.783" end="1:00.183">for</span> <span begin="1:00.222" end="1:01.304">now?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你为谁而买醉？</span></p><p begin="1:01.935" end="1:05.527" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:01.935" end="1:02.127">And</span> <span begin="1:02.127" end="1:02.421">what</span> <span begin="1:02.421" end="1:02.674">they</span> <span begin="1:02.674" end="1:02.908">got</span> <span begin="1:02.908" end="1:03.159">that</span> <span begin="1:03.159" end="1:03.389">I</span> <span begin="1:03.389" end="1:03.644">ain&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:03.644" end="1:03.898">got?</span> <span begin="1:03.898" end="1:04.138">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="1:04.138" end="1:04.634">I</span> <span begin="1:04.634" end="1:04.869">got</span> <span begin="1:04.869" end="1:05.094">a</span> <span begin="1:05.094" end="1:05.527">lot</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">他有哪些我没有的特点？我明明也不赖</span></p><p begin="1:05.833" end="1:09.498" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:05.833" end="1:06.094">Don&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:06.094" end="1:06.324">make</span> <span begin="1:06.324" end="1:06.571">me</span> <span begin="1:06.571" end="1:06.805">run</span> <span begin="1:06.805" end="1:07.058">up</span> <span begin="1:07.058" end="1:07.300">on</span> <span begin="1:07.300" end="1:07.538">&apos;em,</span> <span begin="1:07.538" end="1:07.783">got</span> <span begin="1:07.783" end="1:07.990">me</span> <span begin="1:08.055" end="1:08.279">blow</span><span begin="1:08.279" end="1:08.538">in&apos;</span> <span begin="1:08.538" end="1:08.749">up</span> <span begin="1:08.749" end="1:08.978">their</span> <span begin="1:08.978" end="1:09.498">spot</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可别让我沿路追上他 轰了他的地盘</span></p><p begin="1:09.799" end="1:13.519" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:09.799" end="1:09.981">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="1:09.981" end="1:10.210">I</span> <span begin="1:10.210" end="1:10.473">ain&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:10.473" end="1:10.719">got</span> <span begin="1:10.719" end="1:10.912">no</span> <span begin="1:11.010" end="1:11.287">busi</span><span begin="1:11.287" end="1:11.505">ness</span> <span begin="1:11.505" end="1:11.737">catch</span><span begin="1:11.737" end="1:11.937">in&apos;</span> <span begin="1:11.937" end="1:12.225">feel</span><span begin="1:12.225" end="1:12.507">ings</span> <span begin="1:12.507" end="1:12.930">any</span><span begin="1:12.930" end="1:13.519">way</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我根本不需要在乎内心的感觉</span></p><p begin="1:13.906" end="1:16.829" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:13.906" end="1:14.147">I</span> <span begin="1:14.147" end="1:14.382">ain&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:14.382" end="1:14.664">got</span> <span begin="1:14.664" end="1:14.971">no</span> <span begin="1:14.971" end="1:15.149">busi</span><span begin="1:15.149" end="1:15.389">ness</span> <span begin="1:15.389" end="1:15.632">catch</span><span begin="1:15.632" end="1:15.855">in&apos;</span> <span begin="1:15.855" end="1:16.130">feel</span><span begin="1:16.130" end="1:16.829">ings</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不需要把握什么感觉</span></p><p begin="1:17.250" end="1:18.958" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:17.250" end="1:17.547">Catch</span><span begin="1:17.547" end="1:17.820">in&apos;</span> <span begin="1:17.820" end="1:18.108">feel</span><span begin="1:18.108" end="1:18.958">ings</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">把握感觉</span></p><p begin="1:19.747" end="1:23.671" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:19.747" end="1:19.992">These</span> <span begin="1:19.992" end="1:20.292">girls</span> <span begin="1:20.292" end="1:20.694">only</span> <span begin="1:20.694" end="1:20.918">want</span> <span begin="1:20.918" end="1:21.201">you</span> <span begin="1:21.201" end="1:21.448">when</span> <span begin="1:21.448" end="1:21.679">you&apos;re</span> <span begin="1:21.679" end="1:21.909">win</span><span begin="1:21.909" end="1:22.610">nin&apos;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这些姑娘们只看上了我的功成名就</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:22.701" end="1:23.671"><span begin="1:22.701" end="1:22.811">(Win</span><span begin="1:22.919" end="1:23.671">nin&apos;)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">功成名就</span></span></p><p begin="1:23.671" end="1:27.474" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:23.671" end="1:23.861">But</span> <span begin="1:23.861" end="1:24.090">you&apos;ve</span> <span begin="1:24.090" end="1:24.358">been</span> <span begin="1:24.358" end="1:24.602">with</span> <span begin="1:24.602" end="1:24.873">me</span> <span begin="1:24.873" end="1:25.111">from</span> <span begin="1:25.111" end="1:25.351">the</span> <span begin="1:25.351" end="1:25.585">be</span><span begin="1:25.585" end="1:25.865">gin</span><span begin="1:25.865" end="1:26.421">nin&apos;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可自始至终与我在一起的人是你</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:26.439" end="1:27.474"><span begin="1:26.439" end="1:26.581">(Ooh,</span> <span begin="1:26.581" end="1:26.914">yeah,</span> <span begin="1:27.094" end="1:27.474">yeah)</span></span></p><p begin="1:27.539" end="1:31.231" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:27.539" end="1:27.819">And</span> <span begin="1:27.819" end="1:28.070">I</span> <span begin="1:28.070" end="1:28.291">know</span> <span begin="1:28.291" end="1:28.543">right</span> <span begin="1:28.543" end="1:28.823">now</span> <span begin="1:28.823" end="1:29.063">that</span> <span begin="1:29.063" end="1:29.326">we&apos;re</span> <span begin="1:29.326" end="1:29.531">not</span> <span begin="1:29.531" end="1:29.845">talk</span><span begin="1:29.845" end="1:30.354">in&apos;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我也知道 现在的我们已经疏远</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:30.225" end="1:31.231"><span begin="1:30.225" end="1:30.419">(Not</span> <span begin="1:30.419" end="1:30.668">talk</span><span begin="1:30.723" end="1:31.231">in&apos;)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">已经疏远</span></span></p><p begin="1:31.285" end="1:35.165" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:31.285" end="1:31.426">I</span> <span begin="1:31.426" end="1:31.666">hope</span> <span begin="1:31.725" end="1:31.956">you</span> <span begin="1:31.956" end="1:32.181">know</span> <span begin="1:32.181" end="1:32.440">this</span> <span begin="1:32.440" end="1:32.685">dick</span> <span begin="1:32.685" end="1:32.859">i</span><span begin="1:32.859" end="1:32.994">s s</span><span begin="1:32.994" end="1:33.152">til</span><span begin="1:33.152" end="1:33.413">l an</span> <span begin="1:33.413" end="1:34.296">op</span><span begin="1:34.296" end="1:35.165">tion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">希望你知道 我这里依然可供你依靠</span></p><p begin="1:35.496" end="1:38.029" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:35.496" end="1:35.635">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="1:35.635" end="1:35.934">I&apos;ll</span> <span begin="1:35.934" end="1:36.153">beat</span> <span begin="1:36.153" end="1:36.375">it</span> <span begin="1:36.375" end="1:36.885">up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">届时我会狂欢一场</span><span ttm:role="